Expense CLI using NodeJS

Commands

Create/Add: 
    expense add [cattegory] [price] [payment method]

Show/Read:
    expense show 
    expense show --asc
    expense show --desc

Delete:
    expense delete [id]

Update:
    expense uppdate [id] --update-category [new category] --update-price [new price] --update-payment-method [new payment method]
    expense uppdate [id] --update-category [new category]
    expense uppdate [id] --update-price [new price] 
    expense uppdate [id] --update-payment-method [new payment method]

        or
        
    expense uppdate [id] -uc [new category] -up [new price] -upm [new payment method]
    expense uppdate [id] -uc [new category]
    expense uppdate [id] -up [new price]
    expense uppdate [id] -upm [new payment method]

Sort by price:
    expense price --asc
    expense price --desc

Get by ID:
    expense get [id]